{"tid":909984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嗑藥後與友吵架開槍　他反遭擊中下體慘死","createTime":"2018-11-20T22:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T07:32:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ff14f0cc7965587c89f6f16c4883733bcd426d47","tid":909984,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T22:02:08.000Z","msg":"美國洛杉磯羅斯米德市（Rosemead）當地時間上周三（14日）發生槍擊命案，兩名華裔男子因爭執互相向對方開槍，其中一人下體受致命一擊，傷重身亡；另一人則受重傷送院治療。<br />\n《紐西蘭先驅報》報導，警方指死者為中國籍男子郭揚（Guo Yang，音譯）因受藥物影響產生幻覺，懷疑一同從天津到美國打拚的李姓男子監視他，李男當下否認並與郭揚發生衝突，隨後郭揚持槍朝李男的腿部開兩槍，李男也舉起槍反擊朝郭揚下半身連開數槍，警方趕到時發現郭揚倒地不治，李男則重傷送院治療。<br />\n法醫恩加揚（Frank Ngayan）當地時間上周五（16日）驗屍後，指郭揚身中多槍，但致命一槍為下體要害。警方表示李姓男子因自衛而開槍，屬正當防衞，但案件仍須轉交檢察官決定是否起訴李姓男子。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181121/640_ba04131f0c14c6ff646d168c2bb4d22d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181121%2F640_ba04131f0c14c6ff646d168c2bb4d22d.jpg&h=4a74a90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181121/1470136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470136%2F&d=lYAFvjf5Szr3PiovwE4oNwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=49ed11d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181121%2F1470136%2F&h=a71607b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181121/1470136/</a>"},{"pid":"f7382054fa8d1da427f504a62d92bcc34c40f075","tid":909984,"uid":104443,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T22:08:02.000Z","msg":"世界三大垃圾民族<br />\n無恥泡菜、姦國印度、支那蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇人會可憐佢地"},{"pid":"7ebf7e473e00211e95ed183cd5b5825838472bd2","tid":909984,"uid":83097,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T22:08:29.000Z","msg":"肯定係煙草公司或者trump supporter作既假新聞<br />\n目的係引人屌吸毒<br />\n但連登仔